449
00:33:59,430 --> 00:34:00,590
Tentu saja aku marah.

450
00:34:00,590 --> 00:34:02,300
Namun, kau tidak berhak menegurku.

451
00:34:03,470 --> 00:34:04,310
Lepaskan!

452
00:34:04,780 --> 00:34:05,740
Bu Guru.

453
00:34:07,190 --> 00:34:09,280
Apakah kau suka pria
yang seperti Meng Xu'an?

454
00:34:14,160 --> 00:34:15,280
